721
00:52:07,790 --> 00:52:10,480
I didn't learn from one mistake, and I made another, sir.

722
00:52:10,500 --> 00:52:12,510
You made your decision, son.

723
00:52:12,620 --> 00:52:17,420
Sir, my family, my whole family, was in Buenos Aires, sir.

724
00:52:20,010 --> 00:52:22,690
Is this your signature, Rico?

725
00:52:23,180 --> 00:52:25,040
Sir, yes, it is, sir!

726
00:52:30,230 --> 00:52:32,320
Doesn't look like it to me.

727
00:52:35,080 --> 00:52:38,700
- Carry on, Private! - Yes, sir!

728
00:52:51,000 --> 00:52:55,560
Out of the ashes of Buenos Aires comes first sorrow...

